  <name>XnSketch</name>
  <summary>Turn photos into sketch images</summary>
  <description>
    <p>**This is a community package of XnSketch and not officially supported by Pierre-e Gougelet.**</p>
    <p>XnSketch allows you to turn your photos into cartoon or sketch images.</p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>18 different effects (black strokes, white strokes, pastel, pencil sketch, colored sketch, ...)</li>
      <li>Edge strength, and opacity adjustement</li>
      <li>Contrast, brightness, saturation adjustement</li>
      <li>Save or share the result</li>
    </ul>
    <p>XnSketch is provided as freeware.</p>
    <p>You are granted the right to use and to make an unlimited number of copies of this software.</p>
